{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/01_technology/01_client/web/009_移动端的适配方案/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Vance’s Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"e6189fcc-ea44-5fd1-a272-0b40c02b7a99","excerpt":"1、使用 rem 实现 px 的自动适配 px 是一个固定单位，无关什么设备 px 的单位是一样的。\n而我们有时候是需要等比例放缩，但是又不好使用百分比，所以这个时候需要用 px 自动转换为 rem。 1、安装 postcss-pxtorem 2、设置规则\n在 vue.config.js 中配置…","html":"<h1>1、使用 rem 实现 px 的自动适配</h1>\n<p>px 是一个固定单位，无关什么设备 px 的单位是一样的。\n而我们有时候是需要等比例放缩，但是又不好使用百分比，所以这个时候需要用 px 自动转换为 rem。</p>\n<p>1、安装 postcss-pxtorem</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> postcss-pxtorem -D</code></pre></div>\n<p>2、设置规则\n在 vue.config.js 中配置</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token literal-property property\">postcss</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">plugins</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">pxtorem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// 根字体大小，如果设计图是1366，则这里设置为136.6,</span>\n      <span class=\"token literal-property property\">rootValue</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">136.6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token literal-property property\">propList</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"*\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>3、此时我们正常使用 css 中的 px 就行了</p>\n<p>此时我们写的 px 都会被转换为 rem\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/vance/static/c7a6b91cb9de7042d92383d3c2f25fcd/11fc9/002_eg_1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48.10126582278481%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"eg1\"\n        title=\"eg1\"\n        src=\"/vance/static/c7a6b91cb9de7042d92383d3c2f25fcd/f058b/002_eg_1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/vance/static/c7a6b91cb9de7042d92383d3c2f25fcd/c26ae/002_eg_1.png 158w,\n/vance/static/c7a6b91cb9de7042d92383d3c2f25fcd/6bdcf/002_eg_1.png 315w,\n/vance/static/c7a6b91cb9de7042d92383d3c2f25fcd/f058b/002_eg_1.png 630w,\n/vance/static/c7a6b91cb9de7042d92383d3c2f25fcd/40601/002_eg_1.png 945w,\n/vance/static/c7a6b91cb9de7042d92383d3c2f25fcd/78612/002_eg_1.png 1260w,\n/vance/static/c7a6b91cb9de7042d92383d3c2f25fcd/11fc9/002_eg_1.png 2590w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>4、缺陷</p>\n<p>使用 rem 可以比较轻松的实现移动端适配，但是都是基于宽度的适配，对于高度我们都默认为可以滚屏，但是如果不想使用滚屏效果就需要另外处理。</p>\n<h1>2、使用 vh</h1>\n<p>vh 是解决高度无法做百分比适配的问题的。基本上的浏览器都已经适配了。</p>\n<p>vh 将高度方向分成了 100vh，我们使用 vh 作为单位的时候就可以实现高度方向的布局。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/vance/static/68445ec7d0112aad08d119bd2fc57363/1192d/002_eg_2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.835443037974684%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"eg2\"\n        title=\"eg2\"\n        src=\"/vance/static/68445ec7d0112aad08d119bd2fc57363/f058b/002_eg_2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/vance/static/68445ec7d0112aad08d119bd2fc57363/c26ae/002_eg_2.png 158w,\n/vance/static/68445ec7d0112aad08d119bd2fc57363/6bdcf/002_eg_2.png 315w,\n/vance/static/68445ec7d0112aad08d119bd2fc57363/f058b/002_eg_2.png 630w,\n/vance/static/68445ec7d0112aad08d119bd2fc57363/40601/002_eg_2.png 945w,\n/vance/static/68445ec7d0112aad08d119bd2fc57363/78612/002_eg_2.png 1260w,\n/vance/static/68445ec7d0112aad08d119bd2fc57363/1192d/002_eg_2.png 2662w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1>3、使用布局法</h1>\n<p>可以使用 flex 布局 和 媒体查询</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"移动端的适配方案","date":"July 31, 2022","description":"Vance 对于移动端适配的一点实践"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/01_technology/01_client/web/007_图片预渲染/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"在 Vue 中最快实现一个图片预加载"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/01_technology/01_client/web/008_webpack打包体积分析/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"webpack 分析项目打包体积"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"e6189fcc-ea44-5fd1-a272-0b40c02b7a99","previousPostId":"f4c5d69b-9191-5d48-a390-3d77992815a5","nextPostId":"103ebafb-5218-5716-8d24-ceb43bac